 \"us\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 1904}, {\"ngram\": \"the living origins\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 1930}, {\"ngram\": \"your 'Millionaire' bag\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 1956}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You'd want to bring along nose plugs and high boots to wade through fetid, waste-filled water.\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 2054, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nose plugs\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 1996}, {\"ngram\": \"high boots\", \"from\": 2001, \"to\": 2011}, {\"ngram\": \"fetid, waste-filled water\", \"from\": 2028, \"to\": 2053}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If we go to an indoor tank, also bring a flashlight, because you will not see daylight.\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2142, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an indoor tank\", \"from\": 2067, \"to\": 2081}, {\"ngram\": \"a flashlight\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2106}, {\"ngram\": \"daylight\", \"from\": 2133, \"to\": 2141}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are no blurred lines here.\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2175, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no blurred lines\", \"from\": 2153, \"to\": 2169}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Killing wildlife for a bag is not cool - it's cold.\\\"\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2228, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"wildlife\", \"from\": 2184, \"to\": 2192}, {\"ngram\": \"a bag\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2202}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tagged inPharrell Williams \\u00a9 2025 FemaleFirst Ltd. all rights reserved.\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2302, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tagged\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2236}, {\"ngram\": \"Williams \\u00a9\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2258}, {\"ngram\": \"FemaleFirst Ltd.\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2280}, {\"ngram\": \"all rights\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2291}]}, {\"sentence\": \"duration : 0.33934sv4.2 -2025-12-02 19:00:43\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2348, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"duration\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2312}]}]}"